creator: Kate Seymour MacLean
description:
LibriVox recording of Advent Days and Poems of Remembrance by Kate Seymour MacLean.
Read in English by NoelBadrian; Sonia; John Burlinson; SkyAlbatross; CJ Baars
This is a very short volume of poems by Canadian poet Kate Seymour MacLean, containing only twenty poems. - Summary by Carolin
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
